snippet.title: myPOPGOES Trailer (OUTDATED)
snippet.description:
This trailer is for the original, free, April Fool's version of myPOPGOES released in 2023.
Check out the brand new, super-expanded version on Steam here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2429350

myPOPGOES is an entirely hand-drawn and canon interactive teaser game for the POPGOES series. Featuring artwork by Sian Mewburn (official FNAF artist) and Emil Macko (creator of Five Nights at Candy's).
